
He awoke in a brightly lit place. He was laying in a hammock.
He turned over to see Tiana with her face full of tears as she looked at him smiling."   Shadowman..."   She hugged him with joy.
"   Call me Facilier..."   He accepted the hug with tears.
"   So... How have you been boy?"   Mama Odie calls out from the back bringing some bandages with her.
He shrugs. "   Some bad stuff here and there but nothing as bad as this."
He hisses as Tiana is disinfecting his wounds.  "   Sorry! "   She cringes.
'' Its alright'' He smiles as he drifts off to sleep for his wounds to heal.